OL,3,CFirst case of livestock virus
OL,4,CBluetongue identified in Wales
OL,6,FFrom September 21, the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment allowed all animals who had
OL,8,Fbeen vaccinated against the virus to
OL,9,Fenter Wales. All unvaccinated
OL,10,Flivestock still need a test before
OL,11,Fthey can enter Wales.
OL,13,FDue to cases discovered earlier this
OL,14,Fyear, the UK Government declared
OL,15,FEngland a restricted zone. The cases
OL,16,Fthis week are the first to be
OL,17,Fdiscovered in Wales this year.
